				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Aria of Asceticism quest walkthrough<a name="15957"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 16 04 5:33 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Did this the first day of LoY, and within an hour or 3 of the servers coming up.  
<br />

<br />
All I did was to lull the relevant mobs we dont want adding, then pulled with OOS.  Just pulled to the porch outside the tavern and melee'd him down.  Dropped book first time for me, I ran to Qeynos after remembering where Evanesque was located, then back and bingo!  Had the song.  
<br />

<br />
Was one of the first across all servers to get it - was just lucky I found the troub fast and he had the book.
<br />

<br />
